<refsect1 id="libgtkmm-24-3-desc"><title>&desc-tt;</title>
<para>
libatkmm, libgdkmm, libgtkmm and libpangomm  provide official C++ interfaces
for the ATK, GDK, GTK+ and Pango libraries, respectively. Highlights include
typesafe callbacks and a comprehensive set of widgets that are easily
extensible via inheritance.
</para>
<para>
These libraries follow the official GNOME Platform Bindings release schedule.
This guarantees API/ABI-stability and new releases on a predictable schedule,
delivering C++ API for the underlying APIs as soon as possible.
</para>
<para>
Please note that these C++ interfaces are built with the Sun Studio C++
Compiler and compiled with the -compat=5 C++ compiler option, so version 5
(Standard Mode) of the C++ ABI standard is used.
</para>
</refsect1>
